{
  "texts": [
    "(b) The feature level (intermediate-level data fusion) is used to pick the best set of characteristics for categorization during data analysis.",
    "Using featurelevel fusion, the best combination of features, such as EMG, Respiration, Skin Conductance, and ECG, has been obtained [57,70,167].",
    "(c) The purpose of high-level data fusion (decisionmaking) is to improve decision-making by combining the outcomes of different methodologies.",
    "See Field et al. [49], Ilyas et al.",
    "[70] for more information on data fusion algorithms and applications in body sensor networks.Information fusion has also been achieved in Younis et al. [174]."
  ]
}